blueprint.description:
Original: https://factorioprints.com/view/-Mo7JBWu8gpoG_3jJQrn

Will produce red & green science at speed with stone, coal, iron, and copper.

Small amounts of other items will be produced to create small quartities of other sciences until they can be brought in by train.

Requires "waterfill" (to create plastic) which is easily researched with the small amount of black (military) science that will be available.
blueprint.label: Basic Science
